import React from 'react'
import { Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './Pages/Home'
import Nav from './Pages/Nav'

const Route = () => {
    return (
        <>
   
            <Routes>
            <Route path='/' element={<Home />} />
            <Route path='/about' element={<Home />} />
            </Routes>
        </>
    )
}

export default Route
